data.title: Edouard LeFevre and Marguerite Demers - Marriage Records
data.meta_description: Ancestry.ca has at least 1 marriage record for Edouard LeFevre and Marguerite Demers, among more than 969 marriage records for the surname LeFevre and more than 4690 marriage records for the surname Demers.
data.text:
Ancestry.ca, the largest online family history resource, can help you explore marriage records for Edouard LeFevre and Marguerite Demers from among its billions of historical records from Canada and around the world.

Marriage records are primary resources for the marriage details, since they were created at the time of the marriage. Ancestry.ca collections include indexes that can help you request the record, and in some cases, actual images of the marriage records.
